(885, 676, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"06cbdd9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"structure\":\"22\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"85177df\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":66,\"_inline_size\":68.206},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"389a010\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Qui sommes nous:\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">JCI Tunisie :\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Historique :\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">La Jeune Chambre Internationale de La Tunisie a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 fond\\u00e9e en 1961, et gr\\u00e2ce \\u00e0 sa participation active dans les domaines \\u00e9conomiques et sociaux, elle a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 class\\u00e9e parmi les organisations \\u00e0 \\u00ab int\\u00e9r\\u00eat national\\u00bb par le d\\u00e9cret N\\u00b083\\/115 du 12 f\\u00e9vrier 1983.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">La Jeune Chambre Internationale de la Tunisie est constitu\\u00e9 de 113 jeunes chambres locales et elle est class\\u00e9e premi\\u00e8re en Afrique et Moyen Orient et 8\\u00e8me dans le monde. Elle regroupe plus de 15,000 membres (anciens et nouveaux) appartenant \\u00e0 des organisations locales r\\u00e9parties sur tout le territoire Tunisien.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">En effet, JCI Tunisie est une organisation internationale non gouvernementale dont les membres sont des jeunes cadres influents de 18 \\u00e0 40\\u00a0ans .<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Le si\\u00e8ge mondial de la JCE a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 \\u00e9tabli en 1951 et se trouvait \\u00e0 Coral Gables, en Floride, aux \\u00c9tats-Unis depuis 1969. En 2002, le si\\u00e8ge fut transf\\u00e9r\\u00e9 \\u00e0 Saint Louis, dans le Missouri aux \\u00c9tats-Unis, l\\u00e0 o\\u00f9 la premi\\u00e8re organisation locale fut fond\\u00e9e en 1918.\\u00a0 Parmi les personnes qui ont adh\\u00e9r\\u00e9 \\u00e0 la Jeune Chambre \\u00c9conomique,<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">on peut citer : Kofi Annan - Secr\\u00e9taire G\\u00e9n\\u00e9ral de l\'ONU, Jacques ChiracPr\\u00e9sident de la R\\u00e9publique Fran\\u00e7aise, Bill Clinton - Pr\\u00e9sident des \\u00c9tatsUnis, Frederik de Klerk - Pr\\u00e9sident de l\'Afrique du Sud, Gerald Ford Pr\\u00e9sident des \\u00c9tats-Unis, John Fitzgerald Kennedy-Pr\\u00e9sident des \\u00c9tatsUnis, Yoshiro Mori - Premier ministre du Japon, Albert de Monaco-Prince de Monaco.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/p><div><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/div>\",\"align\":\"justify\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3a6a197\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":31.126},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b259996\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/jci-tunis\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/JCI-Tunisie.jpg\",\"id\":55}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"a7be5bb\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"structure\":\"21\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true},\"content_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1425,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"rgba(168, 168, 168, 0.24)\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"85ea3f9\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":15.969},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"30efb88\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/jci-tunis\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/jci-logo.jpg\",\"id\":53}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f2ad41a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":66,\"_inline_size\":83.696},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"419aa66\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #4472c4; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">JCI Tunis:\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">\\u00a0La Jeune Chambre \\u00c9conomique de Tunis est la doyenne des OLMs (Organisation Locale Membre) du mouvement Jeune Chambre en Tunisie. Elle a toujours prouv\\u00e9 son professionnalisme et son d\\u00e9vouement envers les principes du\\u00a0 credo JCI \\u00e0 travers la qualit\\u00e9 des actions et des formations de 1971 \\u00e0 nos jours\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">par des \\u00e9quipes enthousiastes et vigilantes de l\\u2019OLM.\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p><span id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-70a1befc-7fff-e878-9eb4-df2ee2b532dc\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">En effet, l\\u2019OLM de Tunis n\\u2019a cess\\u00e9, tout au long de ces ann\\u00e9es de diversifier les champs d\\u2019actions. La JCI Tunis, plus qu\\u2019une simple association\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">de 49 ans de carri\\u00e8re mais une famille qui compte aujourd\\u2019hui plus que 100 membres, formateurs et s\\u00e9nateurs. Elle organise des cycles de formations<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">pour les jeunes, des s\\u00e9minaires, des conf\\u00e9rences, mais aussi des manifestations nationales et internationales. Plusieurs th\\u00e8mes int\\u00e9ressants ont fait l\\u2019objet\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 1.2;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">de nos s\\u00e9minaires : d\\u00e9fense des droits de consommation, les assurances, le don d\\u2019organe, la soci\\u00e9t\\u00e9 de l\\u2019information, etc. <\\/span><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"525e7eb\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"structure\":\"30\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":\"15\",\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":\"15\",\"isLinked\":true},\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"15\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"15\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"22a3766\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":33.33,\"border_border\":\"solid\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"1\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"1\",\"isLinked\":true},\"border_color\":\"rgba(211, 211, 211, 0.8117647058823529)\",\"border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"5\",\"right\":\"5\",\"bottom\":\"5\",\"left\":\"5\",\"isLinked\":true},\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"10\",\"right\":\"10\",\"bottom\":\"10\",\"left\":\"10\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"10fa087\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/jci-tunis\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020