-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Que la Foi en Dieu donne \\u00e0 la vie son v\\u00e9ritable sens ;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><br><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Que la fraternit\\u00e9 humaine transcende la souverainet\\u00e9 des nations ;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><br><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Que la libert\\u00e9 des individus et de l\'entreprise assure mieux la justice \\u00e9conomique ;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><br><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Que l\'autorit\\u00e9 doit s\'appuyer sur la loi et non sur l\'arbitraire ;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><br><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Que la personne humaine est la plus pr\\u00e9cieuse des richesses ;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\"><br><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\\\">Et que servir l\'humanit\\u00e9 constitue l\'\\u0153uvre la plus noble d\'une vie.<\\/span><\\/span>\",\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":44,\"sizes\":[]},\"text_align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"dfe43c4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\",\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"20\",\"right\":\"20\",\"bottom\":\"20\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":true},\"content_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":1558,\"sizes\":[]},\"gap\":\"narrow\",\"height\":\"min-height\",\"custom_height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":772,\"sizes\":[]},\"content_position\":\"middle\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/jci-tunis\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/05\\/axe-1.jpg\",\"id\":626},\"background_position\":\"center center\",\"background_attachment\":\"fixed\",\"background_repeat\":\"no-repeat\",\"background_size\":\"cover\",\"background_overlay_background\":\"classic\",\"background_overlay_color\":\"#D9D9D9\",\"background_overlay_opacity\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.87,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"dd9863e\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"43ab728\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Les cinq axes de travail de JCI:<\\/span><\\/p><p><b id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-4514e12b-7fff-573e-b22e-3992c87bf130\\\" style=\\\"font-weight: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">L\\u2019impact<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> : c\\u2019est le changement. L\\u2019impact c\\u2019est l\\u2019action. Changer pour l\\u2019avenir. L\\u2019action pour la soci\\u00e9t\\u00e9. L\\u2019impact pour le meilleur. L\\u2019impact cr\\u00e9\\u00e9 par des citoyens actifs engag\\u00e9s \\u00e0 tous les niveaux de la soci\\u00e9t\\u00e9. L\\u2019impact est le r\\u00e9sultat d\\u2019une action collective.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Collaborer: <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">c\\u2019est l\\u2019union. Collaborer c\\u2019est le partenariat. Union pour des objectifs communs. Des partenaires pour le d\\u00e9veloppement communautaire. Collaborer pour un impact commun.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Motiver:<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> c\\u2019est l\\u2019\\u00e9mancipation. Motiver c\\u2019est la passion. L\\u2019\\u00e9mancipation des jeunes. La passion pour des communaut\\u00e9s plus fortes. Motiver \\u00e0 am\\u00e9liorer le monde. Motivation pour cr\\u00e9er un changement positif. Motiver les citoyens actifs \\u00e0 accepter les d\\u00e9fis.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Connecter: <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">\\u00a0c\\u2019est le lien. Connecter c\\u2019est le r\\u00e9seau. Des liens pour partager des outils. Un r\\u00e9seau pour un soutien plus fort. Connecter les individus, les communaut\\u00e9s et la soci\\u00e9t\\u00e9.<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Investir: <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">\\u00a0c\\u2019est soutenir. Investir c\\u2019est la responsabilit\\u00e9. Soutenir pour faire avancer nos objectifs. La responsabilit\\u00e9 d\\u2019une stabilit\\u00e9 financi\\u00e8re. Investir dans les id\\u00e9es et les efforts des citoyens actifs. Investissement pour un progr\\u00e8s durable. Investir dans le r\\u00eave de s\\u2019associer pour un monde meilleur.<\\/span><\\/p><p><b style=\\\"font-weight: normal;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/b><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\">Les domaines d\\u2019opportunit\\u00e9s JCI:<\\/span><\\/p><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #4472c4; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-